data.description: Don't miss this large, well maintained home. Beautiful new flooring throughout the main and lower levels. With five bedrooms, three bathrooms and 4,230 square feet, this home offers plenty of indoor and outdoor living space. A private deck and large backyard backs right up to the sand rocks with a trail system right out your back door. There is plenty of parking with the oversized heated garage plus additional parking on the circle drive.
